e three medalists\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They held up their flags for the photographers gathered around in one of the lasting Paralympic images.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their flags\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"the photographers\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"the lasting Paralympic images\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frech just watched.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He took mental snapshots of the moment that had not gone to plan.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mental snapshots\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How the mostly empty stadium looked.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mostly empty stadium\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How it felt on that rainy night in Tokyo.\\u00c2 That night, in the Paralympic village, Frech set his phone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s background with an image of the three men who defeated him holding their flags with two words above it.Never Again.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that rainy night\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic village\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s background\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the three men\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"their flags\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"two words\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That moment of disappointment has become his motivation in the three years since.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That moment\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"his motivation\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the three years\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt felt like the origin story for the hero or the villain, depending on which way they go,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the origin story\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the hero\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"the villain\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNever again will I let that happen.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d After winning a world title last summer at the Para Athletics world championships, reporters asked Frech if the win meant that he would change his screensaver.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0909525912283181e-42, \"text\": \"Para\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNever\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"a world title\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"his screensaver\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t waver.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI said, Absolutely not.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will keep that until the day I retire,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t get complacent.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Complacency is the killer of greatness.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Complacency\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the killer\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going after.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I will never change that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech was born with congenital limb differences, missing his left knee and fibula and several fingers on his left hand.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"congenital limb differences\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"his left knee\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"fibula\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"several fingers\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"his left hand\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By age three, he underwent surgery to remove the non-functioning part of his left leg and to transplant a toe from his amputated foot to his left hand.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"surgery\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the non-functioning part\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"his left leg\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"a toe\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"his amputated foot\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"his left hand\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He got his first prosthetic at 11 months.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first prosthetic\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"11 months\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He received his first running blade at age four.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first running blade\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It changed everything.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI remember the feeling to this day,,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd it was epic, it was so impactful.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember thinking,Man, I need to experience this all the time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He took his running blade to school to show his friends.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thinking\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"Man\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"his running blade\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"his friends\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He played sports against his able-bodied peers.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"his able-bodied peers\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in 2013, he traveled with his dad, Clayton, to his first adaptive sports event in Edmond, Okla. At age eight, he competed in track and field at the Endeavor Games and for the first time, his opponents also had physical disabilities.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his dad\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"Clayton\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"his first adaptive sports event\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"Edmond\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the Endeavor Games\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"his opponents\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"physical disabilities\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ezra says his dad put him in each of the track and field events to figure out what he liked best.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 0.9999450334099059, \"rank\": 5.4969611453196596e-05, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his dad\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and field events\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant doing all of the running, throwing and yes, the jumping events.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the running\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the jumping events\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI remember when I high jumped for the first time,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same feeling I still chase to this day, that feeling of freedom, that feeling of soaring through the air.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same feeling\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just genuinely do not think there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a better feeling in the world than clearing a high jump bar.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"a high jump bar\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the feeling I chase on a day-to-day basis.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Eventually, Frech settled on three events as his favorites.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"his favorites\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 100 meters, the high jump and the long jump.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 100 meters\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"the high jump\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They happened to be the three events his T63 classification competes in internationally.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the three events\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years after participating in his first meet, he watched the 2016 Paralympic Games in Rio de Janeiro and told his friends and family that he was going to make the U.S. Paralympic team for Tokyo.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEveryone said I was crazy,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3096, \"end\": 3110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3363837202538486e-26, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first meet\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"his friends\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Paralympic team\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEveryone\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was statistically unlikely.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, an 11-year-old saying he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gonna make the Games in four years is utterly ridiculous.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The COVID-19 pandemic postponed those Games an extra year and Frech made his first Paralympic team in 2021, at age 16.\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those Games\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"his first Paralympic team\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He came within an inch of earning a medal in the high jump, finishing fifth.\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an inch\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3559}, {\"ngram\": \"the high jump\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat is undoubtedly one of the most devastating moments of my entire life,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says now.\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"the most devastating moments\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"my entire life\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s easy to fail in private.\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hard to fail on the world stage where everyone sees it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d That moment, memorialized on his phone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s wallpaper, continues to drive him.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cCompeting at a high level there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s ups, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s downs, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s highs, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lows,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Frech, now 19. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s days I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to train.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 4031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3778}, {\"ngram\": \"it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3790}, {\"ngram\": \"That moment\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3802}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s wallpaper\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"a high level there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s ups\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3912}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s highs\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lows\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I open up my phone, I see the guys that beat me in Tokyo and it reminds me that I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t get complacent and I gotta keep working.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Earlier this year, Frech announced his decision to attend USC and compete on the track and field team.\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4087, \"end\": 4092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"