tence\": \"He is the first above the knee amputee to commit to a Division I track and field program.\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knee\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4543}, {\"ngram\": \"amputee\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4551}, {\"ngram\": \"a Division I track and field program\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hopes that while he may be the first to do it, that others will see him and follow suit.\\u00c2 Ezra and Clayton founded Angel City Sports in 2013 on the track at the Endeavor Games and launched two years later.\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4697, \"end\": 4701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 0.9999450334099059, \"rank\": 5.4969611453196596e-05, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}, {\"begin\": 4722, \"end\": 4732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.116478846281677e-30, \"text\": \"Angel City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4658, \"to\": 4664}, {\"ngram\": \"suit\", \"from\": 4689, \"to\": 4693}, {\"ngram\": \"Clayton\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4759}, {\"ngram\": \"the Endeavor Games\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Team USA Media Summit in April, Ezra recalled standing near the long jump pit during the event when Clayton turned to an official and said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhy are we coming to Tornado Alley in tornado season to run, jump and throw stuff?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The father and son wondered why there were few, if any, adaptive sports available where they lived in Southern California.\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 5172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4820, \"end\": 4828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9981851002069873, \"rank\": 0.0018143099977475164, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4852, \"end\": 4856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 0.9999450334099059, \"rank\": 5.4969611453196596e-05, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}, {\"begin\": 4984, \"end\": 4997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tornado_Alley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.344894917404623e-36, \"text\": \"Tornado Alley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tornado_Alley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tornado_Alley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4850}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump pit\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4914}, {\"ngram\": \"Clayton\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4927}, {\"ngram\": \"an official\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 4949}, {\"ngram\": \"tornado season\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5015}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5048}, {\"ngram\": \"The father\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5059}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"few, if any, adaptive sports\", \"from\": 5092, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"Southern California\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They decided they would bring adaptive sports to Los Angeles.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThink about NBA, NFL, even NHL, NCAA, it comes out of Southern California because we can play year round, right?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Clayton says.\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5252, \"end\": 5255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7025537818729585e-15, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 5257, \"end\": 5260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9993921563952824, \"rank\": 0.0006081852744948672, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 5267, \"end\": 5270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 0.9999998180192217, \"rank\": 1.8074331957547443e-07, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}, {\"begin\": 5272, \"end\": 5276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.999999968079465, \"rank\": 3.192086660183829e-08, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adaptive sports\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"Los Angeles\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5233}, {\"ngram\": \"Southern California\", \"from\": 5293, \"to\": 5312}, {\"ngram\": \"year round\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5343}, {\"ngram\": \"right?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Clayton\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re a sporty culture.\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sporty culture\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then here we are not sending athletes into the Paralympic system, because there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s no programs and there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s no strong organizations, and so that was part of the motivation to start introducing sports.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 The organization launched its first Angel City Games in June 2015, holding competitions in track and field and wheelchair basketball for 125 adaptive athletes.\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5428, \"to\": 5436}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic system\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"no programs\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5494}, {\"ngram\": \"no strong organizations\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5532}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5550, \"to\": 5554}, {\"ngram\": \"the motivation\", \"from\": 5558, \"to\": 5572}, {\"ngram\": \"The organization\", \"from\": 5606, \"to\": 5622}, {\"ngram\": \"its first Angel City Games\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5658}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 5662, \"to\": 5666}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 5681, \"to\": 5693}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 5697, \"to\": 5702}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 5707, \"to\": 5712}, {\"ngram\": \"wheelchair basketball\", \"from\": 5717, \"to\": 5738}, {\"ngram\": \"125 adaptive athletes\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angel City Sports now offers year-round sports clinics in a variety of sports while the Angel City Games have expanded from a two-day event to four days and includes competitions in archery, swimming and wheelchair tennis.\", \"from\": 5767, \"to\": 5989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5767, \"end\": 5777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.116478846281677e-30, \"text\": \"Angel City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 5855, \"end\": 5865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.116478846281677e-30, \"text\": \"Angel City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angel_City_FC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"year-round sports clinics\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5834}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 5844}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-day event\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5906}, {\"ngram\": \"four days\", \"from\": 5910, \"to\": 5919}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 5933, \"to\": 5945}, {\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 5949, \"to\": 5956}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming and wheelchair tennis\", \"from\": 5958, \"to\": 5988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nonprofit also provides sports equipment and competition to people with disabilities year-round.\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The nonprofit\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"sports equipment\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6034}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 6039, \"to\": 6050}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6054, \"to\": 6060}, {\"ngram\": \"disabilities\", \"from\": 6066, \"to\": 6078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frech sees track and field and the Paralympics as a platform for him to normalize and destigmatize disability.\", \"from\": 6092, \"to\": 6202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 6092, \"to\": 6097}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 6103, \"to\": 6108}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6118}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6138}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 6142, \"to\": 6152}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have someone in the mainstream media with a physical disability competing on the world stage.\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 6220, \"to\": 6227}, {\"ngram\": \"the mainstream media\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6251}, {\"ngram\": \"a physical disability\", \"from\": 6257, \"to\": 6278}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the next generation of para athletes, he wants to be that person.\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 6313, \"to\": 6332}, {\"ngram\": \"para athletes\", \"from\": 6336, \"to\": 6349}, {\"ngram\": \"that person\", \"from\": 6366, \"to\": 6377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI would trade in every medal, every world record, every national championship title, if it meant I could normalize disability in the process,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6384}, {\"ngram\": \"every medal\", \"from\": 6400, \"to\": 6411}, {\"ngram\": \"every national championship title\", \"from\": 6433, \"to\": 6466}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 6498, \"to\": 6508}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6523}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat's what I am about, I just know that those accolades are a step to reach that larger goal.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He hopes to see Paralympians breaking into mainstream media like podcasts or sports talk shows.\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6547}, {\"ngram\": \"those accolades\", \"from\": 6584, \"to\": 6599}, {\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6610}, {\"ngram\": \"that larger goal.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6620, \"to\": 6640}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympians\", \"from\": 6657, \"to\": 6669}, {\"ngram\": \"mainstream media\", \"from\": 6684, \"to\": 6700}, {\"ngram\": \"podcasts\", \"from\": 6706, \"to\": 6714}, {\"ngram\": \"sports talk shows\", \"from\": 6718, \"to\": 6735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But most of all, he wants the world to see the athletes for what they are: people with physical disabilities competing at the highest level.\", \"from\": 6738, \"to\": 6878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6764, \"to\": 6773}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 6781, \"to\": 6793}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6813, \"to\": 6819}, {\"ngram\": \"physical disabilities\", \"from\": 6825, \"to\": 6846}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 6860, \"to\": 6877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis is not a pity party for people with disabilities who got active and participated in sports,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Frech says.\", \"from\": 6880, \"to\": 6994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis\", \"from\": 6880, \"to\": 6887}, {\"ngram\": \"a pity party\", \"from\": 6895, \"to\": 6907}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6912, \"to\": 6918}, {\"ngram\": \"disabilities\", \"from\": 6924, \"to\": 6936}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6978}, {\"ngram\": \"Frech\", \"from\": 6983, \"to\": 6988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThese are the best athletes in the world.\", \"from\": 6995, \"to\": 7039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThese\", \"from\": 6995, \"to\": 7003}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 7008, \"to\": 7025}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7029, \"to\": 7038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re just missing a leg.\", \"from\": 7040, \"to\": 70